{{Quote|Ah, Lord Tion, can I help you to some l'lahsh?|Bail Prestor Organa, to Lord Tion|<ref name="Points of Origin">{{SWRadio|Points of Origin}}</ref>}}
'''L'lahsh''' was a delicate beverage that was distilled from the [[Nectar/Legends|nectar]] of [[t'iil]] blossoms<ref name="CSWE">{{CSWECite|II|257|l'lahsh}}</ref> produced on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Alderaan/Legends|Alderaan]].<ref name="AGTTSWU">''[[A Guide to the Star Wars Universe]]''</ref> Each blossom only produced a single drop of nectar, meaning that a single year's vintage took hundreds of thousands of blossoms to create.<ref name="CSWE" /> The nectar had to be picked by hand, and could not be harvested by a machine or [[Droid/Legends|droid]].<ref name="J11">{{JournalCite|11|The Most Dangerous Foe}}</ref> L'lahsh could be cooked in a pot,<ref name="Hostage">''[[Rebel Force: Hostage]]''</ref> and it was distilled after harvesting.<ref name="J11" />

